WEBVTT

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:54.590
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:02:54.600 --> 00:02:56.750
for joining me again tonight. We're

00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:58.150
going to go over

00:02:58.160 --> 00:02:59.990
