00:03:06.880 --> 00:03:08.750
we've been praying over.

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:11.990
You know, it's neat to see what we've

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:14.190
been praying over in the news. I think

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:15.750
it's a lot of fun.

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:17.710
You say, 'Look, there it is. It's in

00:03:17.720 --> 00:03:20.830
