00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:31.030
we went in, praying for the lost,

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:33.510
praying for revival as we saw the

00:03:33.520 --> 00:03:35.830
farmer. And the Lord showed us the

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:38.750
rooster crowing

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:42.150
and the silos full.

00:03:42.160 --> 00:03:44.790
So,

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:47.270
I'll just say this real quick, because

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:49.190
so many people

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:50.190
were saying, 'Brandon, where's the transcript?'We

00:03:50.190 --> 00:03:50.200
didn't

00:03:50.200 --> 00:03:51.990
know what happened

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:53.870
with the transcript, but I got it back

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:55.270
up.

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:57.230
YouTube would not put

00:03:57.240 --> 00:04:00.110
