00:04:00.110 --> 00:04:00.120
the

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:02.230
subtitles for the

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:04.670
hearing impaired, I don't know what

00:04:04.680 --> 00:04:06.870
happened.

00:04:06.880 --> 00:04:08.590
For whatever reason, it took us all day,

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:10.390
and then finally this evening we got it

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:12.550
up for yesterday's video. We

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:14.950
apologize to the hearing impaired, to

00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:18.470
the ones that need the subtitles, and

00:04:18.480 --> 00:04:20.349
for the transcript for the people who don't

00:04:20.359 --> 00:04:21.509
want to pray along; they just want to

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:22.990
know what's going on.

00:04:25.760 --> 00:04:27.510
Let me pray over the atmosphere.

00:04:27.520 --> 00:04:29.630
Father, we pray over our live stream. We

00:04:29.640 --> 00:04:33.190
pray over the airways. We pray over the

00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:35.750
internet feed. We thank you, Lord, that

00:04:35.750 --> 00:04:35.760
it is

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:38.190
uninterrupted and unhindered by any

00:04:38.200 --> 00:04:41.750
satanic or demonic force. I apply the

00:04:41.760 --> 00:04:44.870
blood of Jesus over our internet tonight,

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:47.310
over the

00:04:47.320 --> 00:04:49.150
fiber optics or whatever it's called.

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:50.910
Father, we just thank you. We pray

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:53.150
over the atmosphere. We thank you, Lord,

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:55.230
that the angels of the Lord are here.

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:56.630
They're protecting us, Father, and

00:04:56.640 --> 00:04:58.550
there's no distraction. My thoughts are

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:00.390
clear, and I get everything out like we

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:03.990
need to, in Jesus'name. Amen and amen.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:06.670
All right. As I saw

00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:10.350
the silos last night, I could see silos

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:12.550
that were completely empty. I could see

00:05:12.560 --> 00:05:14.630
the wheat fields that were completely

00:05:14.640 --> 00:05:17.470
full of wheat that was ready to harvest.

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:20.510
As I saw the silos, the silo

00:05:20.510 --> 00:05:20.520
on

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:22.990
the left side hardly got any

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:25.870
grain in it. But as I was watching the

00:05:25.880 --> 00:05:29.550
right silo, it was full, and it started to look like somebody was

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:34.630
pressing it down, and it was

00:05:34.630 --> 00:05:34.640
bursting

00:05:34.640 --> 00:05:36.830
out the sides.

00:05:36.840 --> 00:05:39.670
Why in the vision did

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.430
the harvesters not put it in

00:05:41.440 --> 00:05:43.790
the second silo? I don't know. But in

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:46.790
the vision, the

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:48.470
harvest and the grain were coming out the

00:05:48.480 --> 00:05:49.870
top,

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:52.470
but there was hardly any grain

00:05:52.480 --> 00:05:54.470
in the other silo.

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:56.030
I don't know what that symbolized or

00:05:56.040 --> 00:05:58.150
why that was like that, but I thought it

00:05:58.160 --> 00:05:59.950
was interesting

00:05:59.960 --> 00:06:01.310
because I've thought about that all

00:06:01.320 --> 00:06:03.830
day. 'Why, Lord, did the other silo

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:06.070
not get anything in

00:06:06.070 --> 00:06:06.080
it?'There

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:08.750
was so much more room for harvest

00:06:08.760 --> 00:06:10.750
to be in that other silo, but

00:06:10.760 --> 00:06:12.550
it wasn't in the vision.

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:15.790
As I was watching the farmer,

00:06:15.800 --> 00:06:18.550
he had two

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:20.550
of those metal buckets that you would milk a cow

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:23.310
with.

00:06:23.320 --> 00:06:25.430
He was carrying those buckets

00:06:25.440 --> 00:06:28.430
and was frantic.

00:06:28.430 --> 00:06:28.440
In

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:32.070
