00:06:32.080 --> 00:06:34.790
metal bucket; you feed your animals

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:37.350
with it,

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:39.390
slop your pigs, or collect

00:06:39.400 --> 00:06:42.350
