00:06:44.470 --> 00:06:44.480
short-sleeve

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:46.310
plaid shirt on,

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:48.670
a straw hat with a piece of straw

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:50.190
coming out of his mouth, and he was

00:06:50.200 --> 00:06:52.590
frantic, running around. One person

00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:56.830
running around trying to do farm chores.

00:06:56.840 --> 00:06:58.190
I

00:06:58.190 --> 00:06:58.200
saw

00:06:58.200 --> 00:07:02.550
a dog running on a slender path

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:04.630
that wasn't wide, but it

00:07:04.640 --> 00:07:06.870
looked like a road leading to

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:08.470
this farm.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:10.710
I could see all the grain in the distance.

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:14.230
As we were praying, we were praying

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:16.910
for the harvesters to come forth.

00:07:16.920 --> 00:07:19.110
We were praying last night for the major

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:21.510
harvest that's about to take place, that

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:23.590
the Lord was calling for the harvesters

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:26.030
to come forth. It's time,

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:27.990
