00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:30.150
the laborers are few.

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:32.990
So, we were praying into that last night.

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:35.990
As I was looking into

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:38.030
the nations and praying

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:42.790
for Canada and Asia, I

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.710
