00:08:04.920 --> 00:08:14.110
You know, when you see city lights come on, it's

00:08:14.110 --> 00:08:14.120
a big cluster, looking

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:16.670
like a city is glowing all at

00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:19.390
